			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Sy Safransky</strong></span> is editor of <strong>The Sun</strong>.</p><a href="/contributors/sy-safransky" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
</div>

							</footer>
						</article>


